PASCAL BENCHMARK LISTINGS BM1 to 9 

LISTINGS OF BM1 to BM8 FROM COMPUTING EUROPE JULY 27 1978

NOTE: The branch out of a nested "FOR" 
loop is not legal in Pascal/Z or in MT+


program bm1;
VAR k:integer;

BEGIN
	write('Start bm1');
	for k:=1 to 1000 do;
	write('e');
END.
                             
